<div class="presskit-content">
  <img class="image-inline" src="++theme++hauntedtie.skin/domiverse/images/domiverse_poster_small.jpg"/>

  <p>Domiverse, The ultimate one hit brawler !</p>

  <p>Play as a karate master starfish, a space slug, or a prince sausage firin’ some... BIG LAZEEEERS! Choose one of the 8+ heroes, each with unique skills and try to win the Domiverse Tournament ™. You will dive into a wacky world where each hit kills. Take on your friends in a furious battle to become the King of the universe.</p>

  <hr />
  <h2 id="anchor-description">Description</h2>

  <p>Domiverse, it's like Super Smash Bros and Towerfall having a child.</p>

  <p>Fight in arenas filled with traps and surprises at the heart of a cartoonish sci-fi universe. As in a classic fighting game, every character proposes a specific gameplay and offer an original experience. Range shootings, close combat, slides, rolls, underhand tricks, double jumps, completely cheated movements, there is something for every taste! All this served in a home made pixelart which is enjoyed beyond the galaxy.</p>

  <h4>Awesome features</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>One hit one kill</li>
    <li>Unique skills for each characters</li>
    <li>1-4 players</li>
    <li>8 playable characters + 2 to unlock</li>
    <li>Trapped arenas</li>
    <li>Easy to learn, hard to master!</li>
  </ul>
  <br />

  <h4>You got friends</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Free for all / Team</li>
    <li>Survival</li>
    <li>Ace hunter</li>
    <li>King of the hill</li>
  </ul>
  <br />

  <h4>Forever alone</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Arcade</li>
    <li>Trials</li>
    <li>Ai opponents</li>
  </ul>


